@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>At Shopvia, we prioritize the privacy and security of our customers. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website and services.</p>

<h4>🔒 Information We Collect</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Personal details such as name, email address, phone number, and shipping address.</li>
    <li>Payment information for order processing (handled securely via Stripe).</li>
    <li>Product browsing history and preferences to improve your shopping experience.</li>
    <li>Contact and feedback data submitted through forms or support requests.</li>
</ul>

<h4>📦 How We Use Your Information</h4>
<ul>
    <li>To process and deliver orders.</li>
    <li>To send order updates, promotional offers, and account-related notifications.</li>
    <li>To enhance user experience through personalization and relevant suggestions.</li>
    <li>To respond to queries and feedback submitted by customers.</li>
</ul>

<h4>🛡️ Data Protection</h4>
<p>We implement industry-standard security measures to safeguard your data. Sensitive information such as passwords and payment details are encrypted and never stored directly on our servers.</p>

<h4>📨 Third-Party Services</h4>
<p>We integrate trusted services such as Stripe for payment processing and Cloudinary for image hosting. These providers follow strict data protection standards and do not share your information unnecessarily.</p>

<h4>📝 Your Rights</h4>
<p>You may request to review, update, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting our support team.</p>

<h4>📅 Policy Updates</h4>
<p>Shopvia may update this policy as needed. Any changes will be posted on this page with the latest revision date.</p>

<h6 class="text-muted">Last updated: July 2025</h6>
